<h2>gglorenz: Plotting Lorenz Curve with the Blessing of 'ggplot2'</h2>
<p>Provides statistical transformations for plotting empirical 
    ordinary Lorenz curve (Lorenz 1905) &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F2276207">doi:10.2307/2276207</a>&gt; and 
    generalized Lorenz curve (Shorrocks 1983) &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F2554117">doi:10.2307/2554117</a>&gt;.</p>
